  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>The photo irritation test and the photosensitivity will be measured using UVA irradiation and evaluated according International Contact Dermatitis Research Group (ICDRG) scale. The sensibility will be evaluated according to the skin type.</measure>
    <time_frame>During 5 weeks (i.e. treatment period)</time_frame>
  </primary_outcome>
